result.name: Ask for Alonzo

reviews.text: simply awesome... super friendly and the lasagne was so authentic. restaurant has a great vibe...
Great food and kind staff. Felt much better in Hongkong as an European ;)
Amazing and wonderful food every time! Best Italian food in HK.
Great Bar and Food place. Marco and Thea were Wonderful. Their ambassadors of personality and hospitality.

Great service. Friendly staff.
Very very small brunch portions, maybe because of the limited seats, quiet dinner down time and high rent? Packaged burrata ($168) is signature dish, quality is fair but instead of balsamic dressing, pesto sauce was used in this dish and also on a few other dishes.
